---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import locationsData from '../../../data/locations.json';
import services from '../../../data/services.json';

const loc = locationsData.locations.find(l => l.id === 'logan');

const cityContent = {
  logan: {
    name: 'Logan',
    title: 'Concrete Curbing in Logan, UT | Buzz Co',
    description: 'Decorative concrete curbing for Logan homeowners. 14 colors, 10 patterns, same-week scheduling. Free estimates from Buzz Co Curbing.',
    h1: 'Concrete Curbing Services in Logan, Utah',
    copy: `<p>Logan homeowners know that a well-kept yard sets the tone for the whole neighborhood — and concrete curbing is one of the fastest ways to make that happen. Whether you live near the Utah State University campus, along the tree-lined streets of the Island neighborhood, or up on the east bench with views of Logan Canyon, Buzz Co Curbing delivers decorative concrete curbing that transforms your landscaping overnight.</p>
<p>From the historic homes around Main Street to the newer construction filling in south Logan, we work with every type of property in town. Our crew understands the mix of architectural styles that make Logan unique — the Craftsman-era bungalows downtown need a different curb profile than the modern builds going up along 1000 West. That's why we offer 14 integral colors, 10 stamp patterns, and 4 curb styles so you can match your home exactly.</p>
<p>Here's how we work: call or text for an evening quote, and we'll walk your yard with you to plan the layout. Justin personally reviews every Logan project to make sure the design looks right before the crew pours. Most jobs are scheduled and installed the same week — so you're not waiting around for weeks while your yard sits torn up.</p>
<p>Logan gets real winters, and our curbing is built to handle freeze-thaw cycles without cracking or shifting. The concrete is poured on-site in a continuous extrusion, which means no joints and no weak points. Add our color-matched sealant and your curbing will look sharp for years, even after a Cache Valley winter.</p>
<p>If you're finishing a landscaping project, prepping your home for sale, or just tired of hand-trimming along your flower beds, give us a call. We've been curbing yards across Cache Valley for over 15 years, and Logan is where it all started.</p>`,
  },
  smithfield: {
    name: 'Smithfield',
    title: 'Concrete Curbing in Smithfield, UT | Buzz Co',
    description: 'Decorative concrete curbing for Smithfield homes. 14 colors, 10 patterns, same-week scheduling. Free estimates from Buzz Co Curbing.',
    h1: 'Concrete Curbing Services in Smithfield, Utah',
    copy: `<p>Smithfield is one of those quiet, well-kept towns where people actually take pride in their yards — and it shows. The larger lots, newer subdivisions along the north end, and established homes near Summit Creek all share something in common: homeowners here care about how their property looks. Concrete curbing from Buzz Co gives your Smithfield yard that finished, intentional look that sets it apart.</p>
<p>We've curbed hundreds of properties across Cache Valley, and Smithfield is one of our most active areas. The town's growth over the past decade means there are plenty of newer homes that came with basic landscaping and not much else. Adding decorative curbing around flower beds, tree rings, and walkway borders is one of the highest-impact upgrades you can make — and one of the most affordable.</p>
<p>Our process is simple. We come out for a free evening quote, walk your property with you, and help you pick from 14 colors and 10 stamp patterns. Justin personally oversees every project in the Smithfield area, so you're getting the same attention to detail whether it's a small front-yard border or a full wraparound job. Most Smithfield installs happen the same week.</p>
<p>The lots here tend to run larger than what you see in Logan, which means more linear feet of curbing — and more visual impact when it's done. Whether you're defining a rock bed along your driveway, separating lawn from garden, or creating mower-friendly edges that save you an hour of trimming every week, our four curb styles cover every use case.</p>
<p>Smithfield homeowners have been trusting Buzz Co for years. We're just a few minutes up the road, and we treat every yard like it's our own.</p>`,
  },
  'hyde-park': {
    name: 'Hyde Park',
    title: 'Concrete Curbing in Hyde Park, UT | Buzz Co',
    description: 'Decorative concrete curbing for Hyde Park homes. 14 colors, 10 patterns, same-week scheduling. Free estimates from Buzz Co Curbing.',
    h1: 'Concrete Curbing Services in Hyde Park, Utah',
    copy: `<p>Hyde Park sits in that sweet spot between Smithfield and Logan — close enough to everything, quiet enough to feel like home. The community has grown steadily over the past few years, with newer residential developments bringing in young families who want their yards to look as good as the mountain views surrounding them. Buzz Co Curbing helps Hyde Park homeowners get there with decorative concrete curbing that's built to last.</p>
<p>If you've driven through Hyde Park's newer neighborhoods, you've probably noticed the difference between a yard with curbing and one without. Clean concrete borders around flower beds, along walkways, and around trees give landscaping a finished quality that loose rock, plastic edging, and bare dirt edges simply can't match. It's one of those upgrades that makes the whole property look like someone cares — because you do.</p>
<p>We offer 14 integral concrete colors that go all the way through the curb, not just on the surface. Pair that with 10 stamp patterns — from natural stone to brick to smooth modern profiles — and 4 curb styles including our popular mower-style that eliminates hand-trimming. Justin walks every Hyde Park job before the crew pours, so the layout follows your yard's natural contours.</p>
<p>Our scheduling works well for busy Hyde Park families: call or text for an evening quote when it fits your schedule, and we can get you on the schedule that same week. No drawn-out timelines, no waiting for subcontractors. The Buzz Co crew handles everything from start to finish.</p>
<p>Hyde Park may be a small community, but the homes here deserve the same quality curbing we install anywhere in Cache Valley. We're local, we're licensed and insured, and we've been doing this for over 15 years.</p>`,
  },
  providence: {
    name: 'Providence',
    title: 'Concrete Curbing in Providence, UT | Buzz Co',
    description: 'Decorative concrete curbing for Providence homes. 14 colors, 10 patterns, same-week scheduling. Free estimates from Buzz Co Curbing.',
    h1: 'Concrete Curbing Services in Providence, Utah',
    copy: `<p>Providence homeowners enjoy some of the best views in Cache Valley — nestled along the foothills southeast of Logan, with mountain backdrops that make every yard feel like it's framed by nature. That kind of setting deserves landscaping that measures up, and decorative concrete curbing from Buzz Co is the finishing touch that pulls it all together.</p>
<p>The properties along Highway 165 and up into the Providence foothills tend to feature larger lots with established yards — mature trees, deep flower beds, and generous lawn areas that benefit from clean, defined borders. Our curbing creates permanent edges between lawn and rock, garden and walkway, driveway and planting bed. No more chasing mulch after a rainstorm or spending Saturday mornings hand-trimming along crooked plastic edging.</p>
<p>With 14 integral colors, 10 stamp patterns, and 4 curb styles, there's a combination for every home in Providence. The earth-toned colors are especially popular here — they complement the natural stone and mountain landscape that defines this part of the valley. Justin helps every Providence homeowner choose a color and pattern that works with their home's exterior and existing hardscape.</p>
<p>Our process is straightforward and fast. Call or text to schedule a free evening estimate. Justin walks your property, measures the job, and lays out a plan on the spot. Most Providence installs are scheduled and completed the same week — we show up early, pour the curbing in a continuous extrusion with no joints, and you're walking on it within 24 hours.</p>
<p>Providence is one of our favorite areas to work in Cache Valley. The combination of mountain views, well-maintained homes, and homeowners who appreciate quality craftsmanship makes every project here rewarding. If you're ready to give your yard the border it deserves, we're just a short drive away.</p>`,
  },
};

export function getStaticPaths() {
  return [
    { params: { city: 'logan' }, props: { citySlug: 'logan' } },
    { params: { city: 'smithfield' }, props: { citySlug: 'smithfield' } },
    { params: { city: 'hyde-park' }, props: { citySlug: 'hyde-park' } },
    { params: { city: 'providence' }, props: { citySlug: 'providence' } },
  ];
}

const { citySlug } = Astro.props;
const city = cityContent[citySlug];
const neighboringCities = loc.priorityCities.filter(c => c !== city.name);

const localBusinessSchema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'HomeAndConstructionBusiness',
  name: `Buzz Co Curbing — ${city.name}`,
  description: city.description,
  url: `https://www.buzzcocurb.com/logan/areas/${citySlug}/`,
  telephone: loc.phone,
  email: loc.email,
  areaServed: {
    '@type': 'City',
    name: city.name,
    containedInPlace: { '@type': 'State', name: 'Utah' },
  },
  openingHoursSpecification: loc.hoursSpec.map(h => ({
    '@type': 'OpeningHoursSpecification',
    dayOfWeek: h.dayOfWeek,
    opens: h.opens,
    closes: h.closes,
  })),
  aggregateRating: {
    '@type': 'AggregateRating',
    ratingValue: '4.9',
    reviewCount: '50',
    bestRating: '5',
  },
};

const breadcrumbSchema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
  itemListElement: [
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://www.buzzcocurb.com/' },
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Logan Territory', item: 'https://www.buzzcocurb.com/logan/' },
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 3, name: city.name, item: `https://www.buzzcocurb.com/logan/areas/${citySlug}/` },
  ],
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title={city.title}
  description={city.description}
  canonical={`https://www.buzzcocurb.com/logan/areas/${citySlug}/`}
  geoPlacename={city.name}
  locationId={loc.id}
  phone={loc.phone}
  phoneHref={loc.phoneHref}
  schema={[localBusinessSchema, breadcrumbSchema]}
>
  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <section class="pt-28 md:pt-36 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 font-data text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-warm-muted">
          <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Home</a></li>
          <li aria-hidden="true">/</li>
          <li><a href="/logan/" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Logan</a></li>
          <li aria-hidden="true">/</li>
          <li class="text-dark">{city.name}</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hero Content -->
  <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-dark mt-6 mb-8 text-balance">{city.h1}</h1>
      <div class="max-w-3xl font-body text-base md:text-lg text-dark/70 leading-relaxed space-y-4" set:html={city.copy} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust Signals -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-warm-gray border-y border-dark/[0.06]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 md:gap-14">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path></svg>
          <span class="font-data text-sm text-dark/70">4.9-Star Rating</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.745 3.745 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z"></path></svg>
          <span class="font-data text-sm text-dark/70">15+ Years Experience</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"></path></svg>
          <span class="font-data text-sm text-dark/70">Licensed & Insured</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">WHAT WE OFFER</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Curbing Services Available in {city.name}</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-dark/60 max-w-2xl mb-12">Every service below is available to {city.name} homeowners with same-week scheduling and a free on-site estimate.</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {services.map(service => (
          <a href={`/services/${service.slug}/`} class="group bg-warm-gray border border-dark/[0.06] rounded-card p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-dark/[0.06] hover:-translate-y-1">
            <p class="font-data text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-3">{service.shortName}</p>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-dark mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">{service.name}</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-dark/60 leading-relaxed">{service.description}</p>
            <p class="font-heading font-medium text-sm text-accent mt-4 flex items-center gap-1">
              Learn more <span class="transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
            </p>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Area / Neighboring Cities -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-warm-gray border-y border-dark/[0.06]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">CACHE VALLEY SERVICE AREA</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Also Serving Nearby Communities</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-dark/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Beyond {city.name}, Buzz Co Curbing serves homeowners across Cache Valley including {neighboringCities.join(', ')}, and many more.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        {loc.cities.map(c => {
          const slug = c.toLowerCase().replace(/\s+/g, '-');
          const isPriority = loc.priorityCities.includes(c);
          const isCurrent = c === city.name;
          return isCurrent ? (
            <span class="rounded-none px-4 py-2 text-sm font-heading font-medium bg-accent text-white">{c}</span>
          ) : isPriority ? (
            <a href={`/logan/areas/${slug}/`} class="rounded-none px-4 py-2 text-sm font-heading font-medium bg-gold/20 text-dark border border-gold/30 hover:bg-gold/30 transition-colors">{c}</a>
          ) : (
            <span class="rounded-none px-4 py-2 text-sm font-heading font-medium bg-warm-white text-dark/60 border border-dark/[0.08]">{c}</span>
          );
        })}
      </div>
      <p class="font-body text-sm text-dark/50 mt-6">
        <a href="/logan/" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors underline underline-offset-2">← Back to Logan Territory</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-dark rounded-card mx-4 md:mx-8 my-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="font-data text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gold/70 mb-4">FREE ESTIMATE</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Ready to Transform Your {city.name} Yard?</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-white/60 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Call for an evening quote, and we'll have your curbing installed as soon as tomorrow. 14 colors, 10 patterns, zero hassle.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href={`/${loc.id}/get-estimate/`} class="btn-primary">
          <span class="btn-bg" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="btn-text">Get a Free Estimate</span>
        </a>
        <a href={loc.phoneHref} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-heading font-medium text-white/80 hover:text-gold transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z"></path></svg>
          {loc.phone}
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
